ygData.messageBody:
Hello all you fellow addicts. Well I got my ogre warrior to 53. My
druid (retired) is still at 52, but my Iksar monk is now 36. His
(monk) Dual Wield is now maxed at (252). His highest kick so far is
83 dmg. I got some new weapons for my warrior. He now has Blood Point
in primary and Frostbringer in offhand. He still carries his Lammy
and Goranga Spiked Club, but the combo of BP and FB is an AWESOME
combo. The monk now has Goranga Spiked club in primary and Fist of
Rock in offhand. Hoping to find good 2hb for my monk and start my
training in that soon. All in all things are moving along well. I
hope to see you all soon....I am on Saryrn Server.

Leggo Oribarshu

Defender of Ancient Council
Slave to no god.
